{"tid":1116224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對國家不滿！","createTime":"2019-04-19T18:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T05:36:23.000Z","uid":36961,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f79ec5c3858c88d7801804a074598d2e39ad007","tid":1116224,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:50:24.000Z","msg":"小明打算由A國移民到B國。<br />\n<br />\n　　在出境時，負責辦理手續的A國官員問小明：「你要移民，是因為對A國的教育有不滿嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n　　小明：「我沒有不滿。」<br />\n<br />\n　　官員又問：「那你是對A國的醫療系統有不滿嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n　　小明仍說：「我沒有不滿。」<br />\n<br />\n　　官員再問：「既然你沒有不滿，那為何要離開A國呢？」<br />\n<br />\n　　小明：「因為我在B國可以有不滿。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑唔出"},{"pid":"a79425b9f39cdb581b3ba3c7ae31667d8285d9ad","tid":1116224,"uid":213463,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T19:01:05.000Z","msg":"大力：)@&ldquo;?&gt;&amp;&gt;&pound;_[{+{!"},{"pid":"af0fac74f0085847bd3739fb251e1c529abf9553","tid":1116224,"uid":235174,"like":81,"dislike":4,"score":77,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T19:12:05.000Z","msg":"官員繼續問：「那為什麼不移民去C國？」<br />\n        小明：「因為C國失調」<br />\n        官員：「%@*$%@！」"},{"pid":"bb2deac3665dc87afb7e9f53c3e97e77d9f76eb0","tid":1116224,"uid":247924,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T19:15:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1d16c4d50f722bf7bbe0c87c16199223360da67","tid":1116224,"uid":226296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af0fac74f0085847bd3739fb251e1c529abf9553","tid":1116224,"uid":235174,"like":81,"dislike":4,"score":77,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T19:12:05.000Z","msg":"官員繼續問：「那為什麼不移民去C國？」<br />\n        小明：「因為C國失調」<br />\n        官員：「%@*$%@！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T20:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgm